Sword battle! Have fun with your friend slashing each other until counters overflow!

Default controlls are simple (in braces for gamepad):
* Press 'z' (A) to jump;
* Press 'x' (RB) to bite;
* Press 'c' (LB) to slash;
* Press 's' (X) to toggle block;
* Press (and hold a bit) down to toggle crouch;

Later I will add more players and real graphics, so stay tuned.
